Reasoning: The paper discusses the implementation of ontological engineering methodology in the Computer Science domain for the betterment of knowledge management and representation of associated data. This involves the use of machine learning techniques (cs.AI) to create a learner profile and provide necessary resources, as well as the use of ontologies for knowledge management (cs.LG) and representation (cs.CY). The paper also discusses the design and implementation of a learning management system (cs.CE) and the importance of time management skills (cs.SE) in current learning systems.
